Class TestDataFactory

public class TestDataFactory

This class generates test data used in test classes, mostly for BlazeBite and Firestore classes

Changes

04/03/2021 Initial version.
04/25/2021 Class for creating leads.
05/31/2021 Class for creating FirebaseAuthentication__c.
05/31/2021 Methods to standardize creation of random data.
06/20/2021 Class for creating Bill__c.
06/21/2021 Classes for creating cases, email messages and users.
07/08/2021 Class for creating adjustments.
07/08/2021 Classes for creating invoices, invoice line items and products.
07/08/2021 Class for creating supporting documentation.
07/11/2021 Class for creating StripeTransaction__c.
07/17/2021 Processing fee is populated with a random value for Payment2__c.
07/18/2021 Class for creating Collection__c. Support for generating payment adjustments.
08/22/2021 Mercury access token added to BlazeBiteSettings__c.
08/24/2021 Class for creating BankAccount__c.
09/11/2021 Method createXReferences() moved from class TestData to TestDataFactory.
05/22/2022 New methods to retrieve accounts and contacts created in the @TestSetup method.
07/10/2022 TestPayment2 now sets the field VenueId__c.
02/24/2023 Methods to define or create an account directly in TestAccount class. 02/24/2023 Class for creating ProductType__c. New methods for retrieving records created in the @TestSetup method.
03/29/2023 Class TestBill now calculates Service Fees.
10/20/2023 Classes for creating commission payments, and bill payments.
11/10/2023 TestUser: New methods to set profile and role by name or Id.
11/10/2021 Classes for creating Contract and ContractSignee__c records.
11/19/2023 TestAccount.setTag(): Method to set account tag (field that could be used to retrieve the account with getTestAccount).
12/30/2023 New methods to retrieve users created in the @TestSetup method.
03/03/2024 Open Exchange Rates access token added to BlazeBiteSettings__c.
03/05/2024 Accounts are now saved with a default CurrencyIsoCode__c value of 'USD'.
03/05/2024 Class TestOrder2: Order is now created using the currency of the account if any, otherwise it uses USD.
03/08/2024 Add Stripe service fees for international transactions.
03/09/2024 Method to create the custom settings DatedConversionRatesSettings__c record.
08/26/2024 Account Portal status is now set to 'Active'.
